						| My name is Ricardo Terrazas and this is my own personal website
						| I created it and maintain it myself. I use this as an opportunity to showcase
						| all of my various software projects as well as any other skills I have picked up.
						| I also take this chance to tell a bit more about myself
						br
						br
						| To begin viewing my work, you can click the link at the top or just click the link here &nbsp
						a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg(href='./projects')
							span.network-name View Projects
